OL,6,FAn imam has been jailed for repeatedly
OL,7,Fraping a boy at a mosque in Bradford.
OL,9,FMohammed Hanif Khan, 57, was an imam
OL,10,Fat Bradford Grand Mosque on Sunbridge
OL,11,FRoad when he groomed the victim and
OL,12,Fsexually abused him over several years
OL,13,Fin the 1990s.
OL,15,FKhan, of Blagden Street in Sheffield,
OL,16,Fadmitted multiple counts of rape and
OL,17,Fwas jailed for 13 years at Bradford
OL,18,FCrown Court. He will serve an extended
OL,19,Fthree-year licence period.
